title: Beyonce - Sweet Dreams [Official New Single 2009]
description:
Beyonce - Sweet Dreams [Official New Single 2009] 


ARTIST : Beyonce
ALBUM : I Am...Sasha Fierce
YEAR : Album (2008) Single (2009)
COVER-ART : Included

    Sweet Dreams is in the third set of singles released by Beyonce from her highly successful I Am...Sasha Fierce album. Along with Ego, Sweet Dreams is a hot RnB hit. Originally, the song leaked out several months ago, titled Beautiful Nightmare. Beyonce herself came out and apologized for the leak, saying that the song was a work in progress.

Sweet Dreams has no difference from Beautiful Nightmare with the exception of Beyonce randomly yelling "Turn The Lights On". A music video for Sweet Dreams was released July 9 worldwide on Beyonce's officialchannel.
